  <entry>
    <title>卷积神经网络加速模块</title>
    <link href="/2022/04/13/%E5%8D%B7%E7%A7%AF%E7%A5%9E%E7%BB%8F%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97/"/>
    <url>/2022/04/13/%E5%8D%B7%E7%A7%AF%E7%A5%9E%E7%BB%8F%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="卷积神经网络加速模块"><a href="#卷积神经网络加速模块" class="headerlink" title="卷积神经网络加速模块"></a>卷积神经网络加速模块</h1><h2 id="卷积神经网络介绍"><a href="#卷积神经网络介绍" class="headerlink" title="卷积神经网络介绍"></a>卷积神经网络介绍</h2><p>…..</p><h2 id="硬件加速基本方法"><a href="#硬件加速基本方法" class="headerlink" title="硬件加速基本方法"></a>硬件加速基本方法</h2><p>利用<strong>片内DSP资源</strong></p><p><strong>优化方式：</strong><br>1.减少输入参数<br>2.量化<br>3.并行计算<br>   流水线设计</p><h2 id="模型优化"><a href="#模型优化" class="headerlink" title="模型优化"></a>模型优化</h2><p>常用方法：剪枝、量化、知识蒸馏</p><h3 id="剪枝"><a href="#剪枝" class="headerlink" title="剪枝"></a>剪枝</h3><p>剪枝过程：<br>①训练网络到收敛<br>②设置阈值t，权重小于t的连接裁剪<br>③剪枝后重新训练</p><p><strong>pytorch 剪枝API</strong><br><a href="https://github.com/mepeichun/Efficient-Neural-Network-Bilibili">https://github.com/mepeichun/Efficient-Neural-Network-Bilibili</a></p><p>B站Efficient-Neural-Network学习分享的配套代码<br>[1] Pytorch入门：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av86131672">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av86131672</a></p><p>[2] 神经网络剪枝：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av86253919">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av86253919</a></p><p>[3] 神经网络量化：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av86754124">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av86754124</a></p><p>[4] 知识蒸馏：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av87124082/">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av87124082/</a></p><h3 id="量化"><a href="#量化" class="headerlink" title="量化"></a>量化</h3><p>分类：<br>1、聚类量化<br>2、整形量化 <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/79744430">Tensorflow模型量化(Quantization)原理及其实现方法 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p><h2 id="硬件优化"><a href="#硬件优化" class="headerlink" title="硬件优化"></a>硬件优化</h2><p><strong>局部感受野特性</strong></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/QhgfijlFkIP4A7x.png" alt="image-20220413200737926"></p><p><strong>代码示例：</strong><br><a href="http://github.com/bird1and1fish/Garbage-Sorting-Network-">http://github.com/bird1and1fish/Garbage-Sorting-Network-</a></p><p><strong>系统结构</strong>：</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/Jkvr3PYe9GmC4Xc.png" alt="系统结构"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/bOPqeRakVNploC9.png"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/SPoFbwKu3jDdLt9.png"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/I8rjYEPyqKpc29N.png"></p><hr><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/Q1EtmifNlRrCBkS.png"></p><hr><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/wDMujhKS2zryc9O.png"></p><hr><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/PKJEOGMLouR9dlh.png"></p><hr><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/Nn8dOp1wuHzcMGY.png"></p><hr><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/cB3VYX7FMe2sEDh.png"></p><hr><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/GXj4MiEotxr6wZF.png"></p><hr><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/nmoKQLF7uAbR2I5.png"></p><hr><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/13/o9dxgH5LBZf7FiI.png"></p><p>……</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
